title: Week 3 preview & Falcons vs. Bucs recap
itunes:title: Week 3 preview & Falcons vs. Bucs recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap the Falcons lopsided 56-14 win over the Bucs and preview every other game on the Week 3 NFL schedule.
